Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:18.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:24.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:36.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:48.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:52.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:57.73,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:06.24,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:12.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:17.25,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:23.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:40.75,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,A series of television signals originating\Nfrom within the Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.50,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,piqued Britai's curiosity, and he sent\Na recon vessel to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:47.84,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The three soldiers aboard the\Nrecon ship were astonished
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:51.14,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,by the television broadcast of\Nthe Miss Macross Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.58,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Though their ship was destroyed by Hikaru Ichijo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:02:00.45,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,the soldiers now carry word of their shocking\Ndiscovery back to Britai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:07.00,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,140)}BLIND GAME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So... there, uh, wasn't much cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:06.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so thin and wispy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:15.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of makes you feel hot, like\Nsomething shooting through your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it may be a new enemy weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing as simple as a new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:21.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:26.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! I have no idea what\Nthey're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's most unfortunate that the\Nrecorder was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:32.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we send out another recon unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:36.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As Archivist, I believe it may be more\Neffective to collect samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:37.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captives?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}That's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}There's no way that was a new weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only thing it could have been!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:49.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Conda was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard Warera started it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It had to have been a new, secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spouting garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:57.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:58.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:03.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this! Your work here is finished, so get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:04.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:11.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't address this, and quickly,\Nit could affect the ship's morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:18.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It may entail treating our enemy a little roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:20.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roughly, eh? This sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Exsedol, I'll hear more of this idea\Nof yours in my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:38.78,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Global, having given up on trying\Nto elude the pursuing Zentradi fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.82,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,decides to lift radio silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:44.06,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,With their transmissions no longer\Nbeing jammed by the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.86,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,the crew of the Macross successfully\Ncontacts UN Forces High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:53.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've received a signal from\NUN Forces High Command!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From High Command?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayase, put it on the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:02.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,High Command, you are connected\Nto the Macross. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Global, we must assume the enemy\Nis listening in, so unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:09.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reveal how we're planning to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can say is we're scrambling\Nto get to combat readiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:16.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately... Well, not so fortunately for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the enemy fleet is only pursuing\Nthe Macross for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on how long you've been able\Nto elude them, we've determined
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:26.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,that their combat abilities are not as\Nsuperior as you've suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you are ordered to wear them\Ndown as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's like they don't understand a damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:39.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:42.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So they want us to buy them some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:47.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, why do you suppose the enemy\Ndidn't jam our signal this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:50.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, why now, after they've\Nbeen doing it all this time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably want to get a little\Ninformation about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Information about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki, Max, we're teaming up\Nwith Skull Squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki! You got hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:40.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunsight One, this is Vermillion Leader.\NWe're heading back to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gunsight One.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion Team, you aren't\Nscheduled to return yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One of our planes has sustained damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:51.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damage? Is it so bad that you can't\Ncomplete the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I'd like you to stick to the rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Leader, it really isn't a big...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:06:00.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Juggling the rotation is part of your job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Permit us to return to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're disobeying orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:08.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hayase, didn't you learn\Nanything in the academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no atmosphere out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:14.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The slightest amount of damage means\Nthe chances of us dying skyrocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always someplace safe and warm,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,so you have no idea how rough\Nit is out here, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:23.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lecturing me now?\NWhen did you get promoted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:27.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go, Lt. Hayase. This time,\NLt. Ichijo's decision is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:30.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion Team, I'm ordering you back to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ichijo? You went too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A shot across their bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting... Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it was that Exsedol's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what that walking\Nskeleton is thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:00.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an old-timer on board who's just about to retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Baklorela.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Oigur, when old-timers\Ntry to shoot something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:09.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of times their aim isn't so good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if he tried to fire a warning shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:18.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,it could end up scoring\Na direct hit on the enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he really hit them dead on, it could\Ndo more than just intimidate them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A shot like that is the\Nbest kind of threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:39.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Race ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the necktie I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is. Thanks for the great present!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Who"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A-ha! Are you on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get stood up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is she pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she prettier than we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:19.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A...About the same, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:21.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's really pretty then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That includes you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hikaru Ichijo! Mr. Hikaru Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a Mr. Hikaru Ichijo here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:35.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Mr. Hikaru Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Mr. Hikaru Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:45.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ichijo speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! What's going on?\NWe were supposed to meet at 1:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Hey, haven't I seen her somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her! The girl who won the\NMiss Macross Contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:03.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,My singing lesson is running late,\Nso I don't think I can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:06.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing lesson? Man...\NYou have one today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have been busy since you\Nbecame Miss Macross, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:14.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they suddenly decided\Nthey wanted to make a record!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kent the composer wrote\Na song for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:20.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're finally going to be\Na professional singer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:23.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:27.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Well, see you later! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin's squadron has assembled\Nat the designated position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing will commence in twenty {\i1}sperig{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Countdown start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:53.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Asteroid Pamir has been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:07.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be an enemy military operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the ship to Condition B!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Setting ship to Condition B!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:15.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Asteroid fragments are inbound\Nat 2 o'clock, 40 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful energy signature is\Ninbound on the same bearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Focus the Pinpoint Barrier to starboard!\NIt's an enemy barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Set output to maximum!\NClose the emergency shutters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored shutters are now closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A second volley is coming in fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oigur! The old timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Baklorela, stand by to fire the main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Baklorela is targeting along the central axis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:33.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! An enemy ship seems to be\Ndeliberately changing its aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:37.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're bluffing. It's just a feint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Baklorela has opened fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's headed right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to hit us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier can't take any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! The asteroid fragments!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:13.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I have a report from the\Nobservation team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it will take five hours for the fragments\Nto move away from the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Vanessa, switch over\Nto wide-area radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! The wide-area radar is off-line!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been damaged\Nduring the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the radar control room report?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't raise them, sir.\NThe lines seem to be down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they were able to weather the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:45.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was rather close, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool Kamujin took it upon himself to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:52.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. This will make our\Nnext move that much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:54.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,True enough, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:59.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they're without radar, will they\Nstumble their way toward us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I have a report from\Nthe engineering team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it will take ten hours to\Nrepair the wide-area radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:17.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the radar control room personnel\Nhave all been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:31.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Noshiran team, ETA to point three is seven {\i1}mil{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:34.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Halmesta Team, ETA to point four is ten {\i1}mil{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All teams will be in position in twelve {\i1}mil{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that decoding coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:44.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished, sir!\NWe can transmit at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Broadcast once all Reguld teams are in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:48.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the Captain thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:02.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We could use the short-range radar\Nif we just changed our location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because we don't know\Nwhere the enemy is hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,so we shouldn't go moving around blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if they attack again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:15.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fight here, their radar will\Nalso be useless, so we'll be on even terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:20.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess our captain has actually picked up\Na few tricks over the years!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:39.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It's fine for you! You just sit someplace\Nsafe and order other people around!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"We're out here in a vacuum!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:45.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The chances of us dying are much\Nhigher than in an atmosphere!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa? Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I'm just a little down, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:01.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Do we have a code like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:05.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kim, I'm getting a really strange\Ntransmission from someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So patch it through to the Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just going to be High Command\Ncalling to tell him something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But the signal doesn't look\Nlike it came from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:19.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a signal from someplace\Nthat isn't High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:29.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...name of the Zentradi, we order\Nyou to surrender your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The recent attack was merely a show of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:36.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If... do not wish to be destroyed,\Nyou will surrender immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the enemy fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:41.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...receive this demand for surrender...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough. Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}We repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:52.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We lifted radio silence\Nfor just a few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:54.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}yet they've already deciphered our language.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, how shall we respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:01.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore them. There's no need for\Nus to bother answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:12.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:16.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has clearly hatched some new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, but I'm thinking\Nof sending out a Cat's Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't believe we were\Nassigned to fly escort for you, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Maybe it's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're heading for the flagship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Make for their predicted destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's a sneak attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki, do not pursue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:15.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our orders are to fly escort!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader! Four enemy pods at 9 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:28.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Kakizaki, you stay here\Nand guard the lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max and I will take on the pods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:32.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that to me, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine here.\NGo take care of those pods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And have you fly without an escort?\NAre you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:40.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take care of ourselves.\NStop wasting time and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, that's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:45.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am! Max and Kakizaki, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:55.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, the Cat's Eye has begun scanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the enemy's status?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:00.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to tell with all the rock fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have to move a bit further\Nout, if we want good readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:05.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Change course to 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader! They've launched a recon unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:23.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And they aren't putting their\Nusual effort into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:26.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max! Kakizaki! We're heading\Nback to the Cat's Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we're finally clear of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:36.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too big to be a rock fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:38.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hayase! The enemy is behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy recon unit seems\Nto have had an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:57.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrieve any survivors!\NYou must not kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:03.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat's Eye, respond. This is Vermillion Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:05.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat's Eye, come in! Lt. Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:08.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Hayase, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The retrieval team has found a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:25.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They are now landing in the lower hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:36.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo, forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max! Kakizaki! We're going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up, Leader!\NI don't have much reserve ammunition!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:20.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're all\Nblatantly disobeying orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hardly the time to talk about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:24.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy troops have infiltrated the lower hangar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They've probably come to rescue the captive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Britai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:35.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I'm out of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:38.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's time to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hayase, get away quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki, fire a missile at the bulkhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:35.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:38.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the airlock with your lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:41.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, before more enemy soldiers come!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:44.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:48.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can thank me later. Now would you\Nmind please putting me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:54.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our Leader is helpless when\Nhe's around the Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:55.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:08.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I'm about to overheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:11.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, switch places with Kakizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:15.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we're able to make it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.42,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.42,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,469)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:44.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru, Misa, Max, and Kakizaki have\Nbeen captured by the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:48.65,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and are taken out of our solar system\Ninto the depths of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:54.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,There, they learn the shocking true\Nnature of the Zentradi Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.65,0:23:58.19,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:01.66,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"FIRST CONTACT"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.98,0:24:02.48,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(95,144)}FIRST CONTACT
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.17,0:24:22.57,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:28.97,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.19,0:24:35.93,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, We all keep running until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:43.98,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.55,0:24:49.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.25,0:24:56.91,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.12,0:25:04.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.65,0:25:14.57,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
